metadata.name: Road Warrior: Turtle Art Car
metadata.description: Artist: BekxArt, Series: Road Warrior, Edition: Turtle Art Car 1:1, IRL medium: Acrylic, Design: Abstract, Story: Whimsical party Poem

attributes.trait_type: An NFT created from an IRL acrylic painting.  My Road warrior car
with a turtle head and a DJ Bar. It has a giant seat
and big fat tires made of steel.  There is also a dance floor
and it plays music everyone likes.  Let's GO!!
